  "detailed_description": "<strong>Unique Fusion of FPS and MOBA (Pre-Alpha)</strong><br><br><strong>Join us in the creation of Stories One, where the frenetic action of an FPS meets the strategic depth of a MOBA. In this pre-alpha stage, we invite you to experience and help shape this 5v5 PvP arena. Your aim, your strategy, and your feedback are pivotal to the game's development.</strong><br><br><u>Cooperative Team Play</u><br><br>Teamwork is the essence of Stories One. Assemble your squad, plan your attack on the two lanes leading to the enemy base, and work together to dismantle their defenses while protecting your own.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2494370/extras/a56f60226a33f3febee7c3b089a1b44d.poster.avif?t=1694765961\" width=588 height=288 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2494370/extras/a56f60226a33f3febee7c3b089a1b44d.webm?t=1694765961\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2494370/extras/a56f60226a33f3febee7c3b089a1b44d.mp4?t=1694765961\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><u>Arsenal and Special Powers</u><br><br>Choose from five unique weapons and special powers to create the perfect loadout for your playstyle. Coordinate with your team, strategize, and use your arsenal effectively to lay waste to enemy defenses and seize victory.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2494370/extras/e84429b4ef9c08771ba1c6f68d3cc8b7.poster.avif?t=1694765961\" width=600 height=260 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2494370/extras/e84429b4ef9c08771ba1c6f68d3cc8b7.webm?t=1694765961\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2494370/extras/e84429b4ef9c08771ba1c6f68d3cc8b7.mp4?t=1694765961\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2494370/extras/8cca23fa4949248b7d3deef277e3ae89.poster.avif?t=1694765961\" width=600 height=280 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2494370/extras/8cca23fa4949248b7d3deef277e3ae89.webm?t=1694765961\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2494370/extras/8cca23fa4949248b7d3deef277e3ae89.mp4?t=1694765961\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><u>Strategic Deck Building and Leveling Up</u><br><br>Harness the power of a well-built deck to enhance your character's stats and abilities. Gain levels by destroying enemy turrets, eliminating rival players or their robotic minions, and choose cards from your deck to get the upper hand. The better you perform, the more powerful you become.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2494370/extras/3722ab73f5fccac7d33f9d2bd8202500.poster.avif?t=1694765961\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2494370/extras/3722ab73f5fccac7d33f9d2bd8202500.webm?t=1694765961\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2494370/extras/3722ab73f5fccac7d33f9d2bd8202500.mp4?t=1694765961\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2494370/extras/efc280df9f6ace141fe397cdf9d5fe6f.poster.avif?t=1694765961\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2494370/extras/efc280df9f6ace141fe397cdf9d5fe6f.webm?t=1694765961\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2494370/extras/efc280df9f6ace141fe397cdf9d5fe6f.mp4?t=1694765961\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><u>Reward System and In-Game Shop</u><br><br>Every victory brings you points to spend in our in-game shop. Purchase new cards, customize your deck (up to 15 cards), and come up with fresh strategies for each game.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2494370/extras/629a3a68a2b49822973f7579f65211f7.poster.avif?t=1694765961\" width=600 height=308 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2494370/extras/629a3a68a2b49822973f7579f65211f7.webm?t=1694765961\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2494370/extras/629a3a68a2b49822973f7579f65211f7.mp4?t=1694765961\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><u>Personalized Avatar Customization</u><br><br>Dive deeper into the world of Stories One with extensive avatar customization options. Craft a unique identity for your university student as they navigate the challenges of the battlefield. From clothing and accessories to distinct facial features, make your mark and stand out in every match. Your style, your statement.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2494370/extras/4ea83ffec2027cb5b2c8258dd8343394.poster.avif?t=1694765961\" width=460 height=244 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2494370/extras/4ea83ffec2027cb5b2c8258dd8343394.webm?t=1694765961\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2494370/extras/4ea83ffec2027cb5b2c8258dd8343394.mp4?t=1694765961\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><br><strong>Join us on this exciting journey to build a game that transcends traditional genres, blending strategy, team play, and fast-paced shooter action. Stories One is in its early stages and we're looking for players like you to help shape its future. Together, we can craft a truly remarkable gaming experience. Your story starts here.</strong>",
  "about_the_game": "<strong>Unique Fusion of FPS and MOBA (Pre-Alpha)</strong><br><br><strong>Join us in the creation of Stories One, where the frenetic action of an FPS meets the strategic depth of a MOBA. In this pre-alpha stage, we invite you to experience and help shape this 5v5 PvP arena. Your aim, your strategy, and your feedback are pivotal to the game's development.</strong><br><br><u>Cooperative Team Play</u><br><br>Teamwork is the essence of Stories One. Assemble your squad, plan your attack on the two lanes leading to the enemy base, and work together to dismantle their defenses while protecting your own.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2494370/extras/a56f60226a33f3febee7c3b089a1b44d.poster.avif?t=1694765961\" width=588 height=288 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2494370/extras/a56f60226a33f3febee7c3b089a1b44d.webm?t=1694765961\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2494370/extras/a56f60226a33f3febee7c3b089a1b44d.mp4?t=1694765961\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><u>Arsenal and Special Powers</u><br><br>Choose from five unique weapons and special powers to create the perfect loadout for your playstyle. Coordinate with your team, strategize, and use your arsenal effectively to lay waste to enemy defenses and seize victory.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2494370/extras/e84429b4ef9c08771ba1c6f68d3cc8b7.poster.avif?t=1694765961\" width=600 height=260 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2494370/extras/e84429b4ef9c08771ba1c6f68d3cc8b7.webm?t=1694765961\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2494370/extras/e84429b4ef9c08771ba1c6f68d3cc8b7.mp4?t=1694765961\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2494370/extras/8cca23fa4949248b7d3deef277e3ae89.poster.avif?t=1694765961\" width=600 height=280 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2494370/extras/8cca23fa4949248b7d3deef277e3ae89.webm?t=1694765961\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2494370/extras/8cca23fa4949248b7d3deef277e3ae89.mp4?t=1694765961\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><u>Strategic Deck Building and Leveling Up</u><br><br>Harness the power of a well-built deck to enhance your character's stats and abilities. Gain levels by destroying enemy turrets, eliminating rival players or their robotic minions, and choose cards from your deck to get the upper hand. The better you perform, the more powerful you become.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2494370/extras/3722ab73f5fccac7d33f9d2bd8202500.poster.avif?t=1694765961\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2494370/extras/3722ab73f5fccac7d33f9d2bd8202500.webm?t=1694765961\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2494370/extras/3722ab73f5fccac7d33f9d2bd8202500.mp4?t=1694765961\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2494370/extras/efc280df9f6ace141fe397cdf9d5fe6f.poster.avif?t=1694765961\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2494370/extras/efc280df9f6ace141fe397cdf9d5fe6f.webm?t=1694765961\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2494370/extras/efc280df9f6ace141fe397cdf9d5fe6f.mp4?t=1694765961\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><u>Reward System and In-Game Shop</u><br><br>Every victory brings you points to spend in our in-game shop. Purchase new cards, customize your deck (up to 15 cards), and come up with fresh strategies for each game.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2494370/extras/629a3a68a2b49822973f7579f65211f7.poster.avif?t=1694765961\" width=600 height=308 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2494370/extras/629a3a68a2b49822973f7579f65211f7.webm?t=1694765961\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2494370/extras/629a3a68a2b49822973f7579f65211f7.mp4?t=1694765961\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><u>Personalized Avatar Customization</u><br><br>Dive deeper into the world of Stories One with extensive avatar customization options. Craft a unique identity for your university student as they navigate the challenges of the battlefield. From clothing and accessories to distinct facial features, make your mark and stand out in every match. Your style, your statement.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2494370/extras/4ea83ffec2027cb5b2c8258dd8343394.poster.avif?t=1694765961\" width=460 height=244 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2494370/extras/4ea83ffec2027cb5b2c8258dd8343394.webm?t=1694765961\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2494370/extras/4ea83ffec2027cb5b2c8258dd8343394.mp4?t=1694765961\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><br><strong>Join us on this exciting journey to build a game that transcends traditional genres, blending strategy, team play, and fast-paced shooter action. Stories One is in its early stages and we're looking for players like you to help shape its future. Together, we can craft a truly remarkable gaming experience. Your story starts here.</strong>",
